	<text>
		<body>
				<p>May <del>&#63;</del> God grant his holy blessing on the eve of his holy <date>Sabbath</date> to him<lb/> who occupies himself in His holy work&#44; by spreading new light&#44; that is<lb/> my friend and my dear&#44; the wise and the talented&#44; our teacher&#44; <persName><sic>UriLippman</sic><lb/> Leeser</persName>.</p>
				<p>Dear friend&#58;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">In spite of great stress&#44; I am continuing to send you the<lb/> promised work. You will&#44; no doubt&#44; find your way through the dark forest.<lb/> On <date>Monday</date>&#44; you will receive the end five sheets. Now&#44; please note&#58;</p>
				<p>1. That&#44; wherever possible&#44; you begin your translation at the same time.<lb/> Should this be impossible&#44; then the translation&#44; which you will announce<lb/> at the same time&#44; must follow in the <date>January</date> issue. In any event&#44; the<lb/> German text must be in the <date>December</date> issue&#44; along with that which I am<lb/> still to send you.</p>
				<p>2. Please see to it yourself that there are no mistakes in it.</p>
				<p>3. I have myself marked the sheets with numbers. Please observe this.</p>
				<p>4. Note what must be added at the end of page three and that which is marked<lb/> with the number 4. It belongs to the text. Here I must ask you again<lb/> to be exact&#44; since that which belongs to&#44; &#8220;Developing Legends is writ&#45;<lb/>en above&#44; and then there follows the statement&#44; &#8220;Were and are frequent&#45;<lb/>ly history&#8221;&#44; conclusion against <persName>Wise</persName> and his cronies.</p>
				<p>5. The note&#44; &#8220;<persName>Ewald</persName>&#44; etc.&#8221; you will put in the proper place until &#8220;Of all <lb/> nations&#8221;.</p>
				<p>6. In any event&#44; I must have the proof sheets.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I think that I have properly disposed of <persName>Jost</persName>&#44; and have char&#45;<lb/>acterized his entire point of view from the beginning.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I ask for a quick response.</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">Your friend and admirer&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(6)"><persName role="author">Jonah Bondi</persName></p>
				<p>Please attend to the matter of the express charges in the near future.</p>
		</body>
